  <section class="prog-cta">
    <div class="container prog-cta__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get Started</p>
      <h2 class="prog-cta__heading">Not sure which programme is right?</h2>
      <p class="prog-cta__sub">Book a free diagnostic assessment and trial lesson. We will recommend the right programme and pace for your child &mdash; no obligations.</p>
      <div class="prog-cta__actions">
        <a href="/contact/" class="prog-cta__btn prog-cta__btn--primary">Book a Free Trial</a>
